	<article class="post-626461 post type-post status-publish hentry category-mergers-acquisitions category-telecommunications tag-brazil tag-cellular-telephones tag-global-village-telecom tag-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures tag-oi-sa tag-telecom-italia-spa tag-telefonica-sa tag-telephones-and-telecommunications tag-vivendi-universal tag-wireless-communications des-cellular-telephones des-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures des-telephones-and-telecommunications des-wireless-communications org-global-village-telecom org-oi-sa org-telecom-italia-spa org-telefonica-sa org-vivendi-universal geo-brazil news_keywords-brazil news_keywords-global-village-telecom news_keywords-mergers-and-acquistions news_keywords-mobile-phone news_keywords-oi news_keywords-telecommunication news_keywords-wireless-2" id="post-626461">
